Well, I figured it was about time I updated. Today was the first day of school here. About time, huh? It went alright, coulda been better. My feet were killing me the whole day though because I wore crappy shoes =/. I have some pretty sweet classes like Italian, and my last period I could leave if I wanted to. yay. I'm increddibly tired though, so Im thinking of heading of to sleep. Hmmm. I broke up with my boyfriend, that's new news. I'm sick of guys lately, really. Relationships can go down the tubes in an instant, but what do I know. I need sleep, and this damn hurricane is really getting to me.


Goodnight.
=) <♥3

i havent updated in sometime. alot has been going on i guess, im kinda mixed up about a couple guys in my life, but ehh ill deal. i was reading ppls ljs, and it kinda made me sad caz i feel like im loosing grip or idk everyones changing and so am i i guess, i just dont want it. i still have 20 some days left of school. pretty lame. some ppl suggested i should start a band with my piano skills. maybe? idk. idk alot actually, like about this summer. i hate the pressure that im gonna have to choose n stuff, but im not gonna let it get to me ill just see. im starting a job sat working at my uncles appliance store. woo hoo! alright id go on, but im leaving to walmart n gonna go downtown or something. peace ♥

so, this week went fast. yea, it deff. did. and i wish i coulda hung out with everyone and saw ppl more. sorry about that. id name everyone i saw n love, but u no who u r ha. so, the beggining of this week i was in connecticut, doing the usual downtown stuff, then tue i came to florida, and im still here right now. i got my belly button pierced, got some new clothes, and was sad that hannahs party was canceled. kyle n megan n them went to the beach today, hope they had fun. last night at like 2 in the morning, i went with my friend jessica and ross to lazer bowling. in case ur wondering, that would be where u bowl with like black lights n shit. it was deff. cool yo, minus the part that we paid for like 3 games n the lady had to bitch about giving us our money back. a couple times this week, i went to gjhs to see ppl, i wish i coulda gone more. butttttttt, over all, i had a pretty damn good time in fl, and i dont want to leave. really. i wish someone could hold me hostage.itd solve my problems. mannnn.the only thing im looking forward to doing in connecticut is going to a concert of fbtmof, underoath, the chariot, n some othhers. alright im done shittalking. ha. <3 ♥

alright, ill be there in 10 days, and if u want to skip school to hang out or do something on the weekend, thatd be just dandy. this weekened was mad boring. i chilled with the family, my brother came from new york. i played friz-b (how the hell do u spell that?) and sweated my ass off. hmm the most exciting things i did this weekend was learn open arms by journey on piano.wow huh. i wish i coulda gone to a battle of the bands thing this weekend. alot of hard core good bands. i realized that connecticut is really similar to florida. the main difference is my moms yelling. i might highlight my hair. clark, u made me update, ur fricken awesome ok? gosh.:). teddy helped me stay unbored today, thank u.<3 bye guys <33
